We hope to show more of what it takes to set up a successful farm and what we do when we are not sitting in a tree stand hunting. Whether you hunt public ground, have permission to hunt private land, or own your own land, whether it's 5, 50, or 5000 acres, we hope you can find some useful information to help you become a better hunter and land manager. I want to emphasize that our way isn't necessarily the best way or the only way, it's just what has worked for us the last 20 years here at The Bearded Buck.
